 repology/parsers/parsers/crux.py | 67 +++++------------------
 repos.d/crux.yaml                | 94 +++-----------------------------
 2 files changed, 21 insertions(+), 140 deletions(-)

diff --git a/repology/parsers/parsers/crux.py b/repology/parsers/parsers/crux.py
